Release Notes: ----------------------------------------- 2.0.2.1 Added support for rounded corners in Windows 11
2.0.1.6 Minor Bugs Fixes Added windows snapping/sticking to edges of screen
2.0.1.3 Added ability that should intelligently recognize any updates to WhatsApp, and should in theory, be able to grab new messages without needing to further improve Jumble
2.0.1.2 Fixed bugs with WhatsApp to support newer versions Added events to systray icon
2.0.1.1 Fixed flickering system tray icon Updated Strikethrough and Remove Formatting buttons
2.0.1.0 Fixed More Button flyout menu to match themes
2.0.0.9 Added ability to change App Skin / Theme
2.0.0.8 Made some minor visual improvements Improved minor functionality in overall app (i.e. Google account buttons, loading of various webpages, etc.) Improved WhatsApp stability
2.0.0.7 Added completely customizable Icons: Image, URL, Name Added settings to load apps on app startup
2.0.0.6 Added ability for all external links to open with default web browser
2.0.0.5 Added option to see if update is available and to click to update
2.0.0.4 Fixed tooltip on mouse hover over Gmail icon: corrected wrong wording from WhatsApp to Gmail
2.0.0.3 Added load at system startup Added this textbox to disaply release notes Added textbox to display open source licenses
2.0.0.2 Added option to allow/disable loading certain webpages via checkboxes
2.0.0.1 Added option to customize 4 URLs
2.0.0.0 Made new version of Jumble, starting from scratch; replacing Jumble 1.0
